---
eleventyNavigation:
  key: breadcrumb
  title: Breadcrumb
metadata:
  title: Breadcrumb
  description: O Breadcrumb permite a exibição de forma ordenada da hierarquia das páginas e subpáginas de sessões do site.
---

<h1>{{ metadata.title | e | safe }}</h1>
<p>{{ metadata.description | e | safe }}</p>
<section class="py-4">
  <h2>Exemplo</h2>
  {% set navPages = collections.all | eleventyNavigationBreadcrumb(page.fileSlug, { includeSelf: true }) %}
  {% Breadcrumb { eleventyBreadcrumbs: navPages, currentPageUrl: page.url } %}{% endBreadcrumb %}
</section>
